age: 16...
body:
y’all know I had to do it,,,,, hell yeah it’s my spidersona that no one asked for babey

• name: ‘Eesha Emperor

age: 16

occupation: Spider-Man also a Cashier & Truck Unloader at Walgreens

• she can’t see very well after being bit, but it’s not the worst so she still tries to wear her normal contacts.

• her vision only focuses perfectly when she has a adrenaline rush or her spidey senses are triggered.

• falls and slips a lot, the bottoms of her shoes just feel really wet and she’ll just slide and tumble around out of no where. But this doesn’t happen on and surfaces that aren’t the ground.

• her webs produce natural out of a small cut in her wrist, yes that’s gross and weird but she’s a dumb ass and can’t figure out how to make webfluid, also sounds expensive.

•hardly knows how to fight but is a heavy hitter when actually executing a attack.

(edit: here’s a link to some edits I made with her)
